<title xmlns:i18n="http://apache.org/cocoon/i18n/2.1">Global Cambrian trilobite palaeobiogeography assessed using parsimony analysis of endemicity</title>
<link rel="schema.DCTERMS" href="http://purl.org/dc/terms/" />
<link rel="schema.DC" href="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" />
<meta name="DC.creator" content="Alvaro, Javier J." />
<meta name="DC.creator" content="Ahlberg, Per" />
<meta name="DC.creator" content="Babcock, Loren E." />
<meta name="DC.creator" content="Bordonaro, Osvaldo Luis" />
<meta name="DC.creator" content="Choi, Duck K." />
<meta name="DC.creator" content="Cooper, Roger A." />
